109  unsigned getISAEncoding() override {
110  // ARM/Darwin adds ISA to the DWARF info for each function.
111  if (!Subtarget->isTargetMachO())
112  return 0;
113  return Subtarget->isThumb() ?
114  ARM::DW_ISA_ARM_thumb : ARM::DW_ISA_ARM_arm;
115  }
